features: SAFETY NSF STAINLESS STEEL OVERSHELF: Certified through NFC, ensures its suitability for household, commercial kitchen, restraunt, and other industrial uses. The #201 stainless steel material of the table exhibits corrosion resistance, high strength, and durability. Its smooth surface makes cleaning quick and easy, saving you valuable time.

STRONG LOAD CAPACITY: The upper shelf can bear 480lbs, and the lower shelf can bear 280lbs. The Kuarbarr stainless steel double-layer overshelves provide ample storage space and can withstand a certain amount of weight.

ADJUSTABLE HEIGHT: The dimensions of the overshelf are 12" x 60", making it suitable for a 60" stainless steel prep table. The height of the lower shelf is adjustable, allowing you to customize it according to your needs.

Easy Assembly: With all the necessary accessories included, you can effortlessly install the overshelf on your prep table or any desired location without wasting much time. We offer 24/7 customer service to assist you. If you have any questions or concerns regarding the product, please don't hesitate to contact us.

BEYOND THE KITCHEN: The double overshelf offers versatility for a range of applications. It is not limited to home kitchen use and can be employed in various settings. If you are looking to expand your storage space, consider this sturdy, easy-to-clean, and durable overshelf.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High quality shelving best for commercial applications.
reviews.reviewText: I'm using these on the back of my workbench in the garage. Yes, these are overkill but I don't have to worry about them bending or breaking with all the tools and equipment I have loaded on them.Are these expensive? Yes. Are they too expensive? Commercial shelving such as in kitchens need to withstand lots of abuse and still be cleanable to satisfy safety standards. So for that environment, the cost is reasonable. For home use though, less expensive options exist.These are high quality shelves without doubt. I just wish they had included a piece of paper with the assembly instructions on it so I didn't have to save and print out an image from the product page :-(

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars No instructions included
reviews.reviewText: These are nice shelves, but they didn't come with any instructions at all. Which made for a frustrating assembly process. There's also a white stripe running down the center of both shelves I couldn't pull off, so I'm guessing it's supposed to be there? It's not shown in the listing photos. I was able to assemble this by zooming in on the listing photos to figure out how the bolts are supposed to be put in place. Another thing to note was that some of the holes on the legs were not fully punched out, so I couldn't put the lower shelf at the level I wanted, because I didn't have the strength to punch the hole open. These can hold a lot, and I was able to replace two different shelves in my art room with this single shelving unit. Just wish it was made better and came with instructions.
